<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Containing SH — Scrabble Digraph Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">SH is the sibling digraph to CH — equally productive but with different strengths. S is worth only 1 point and H adds 4, giving SH a 5-point base. What SH lacks in raw tile value, it makes up in sheer versatility: over 600 valid words across every position on the board.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">SH by the Numbers</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">5 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">S(1) + H(4) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">600+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid SH words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">S tiles in bag</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>S is the most versatile tile in Scrabble — it pluralizes any word. Using it in an SH word means sacrificing that flexibility, so only play SH when the score justifies the cost (10+ points above your next best play).</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring SH Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
  <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
    <thead class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <tr>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Word</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Points</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Length</th>
        <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Notes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">SQUASH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">18</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Q(10) boosts massively</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">SHRIMP</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">M(3) + P(3) value</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">THRASH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Double H value</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">SHADOW</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">W(4) adds value</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">BISHOP</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">B(3) + P(3)</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">SHIVER</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3">V(4) contributes</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">CUSHION</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Bingo candidate</td></tr>
      <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono font-bold">VANQUISH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-amber-600 font-bold">23</td><td class="px-4 py-3">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Q + V + bingo</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

